boxplot(numeric)

pairs(numeric, main="Olive Oil Metrics", labels = colnames(numeric)[1:11])

hist(numeric$s_yellow)

means = c()
for(column in numeric){
  means = c(means, mean(column))
}

print(means)
##  [1] 50.8750000 33.5125000 12.3312500 80.8125000 78.1937500 47.9750000
##  [7]  0.3118750 13.2525000  1.7082500  0.1181438 -0.0017500
medians = c()
for(column in numeric){
  medians = c(medians, median(column))
}

print(medians)
##  [1] 52.8000 31.1500 10.8000 80.4000 77.2000 47.5000  0.2600 12.4000  1.6535
## [10]  0.1160 -0.0020
diff = c()
for(i in 1:11){
  diff = c(diff, means[i] - medians[i])
}

print(diff)
